{"recipe_desc": "You'll want to let go that Eggo once you've had these waffles. They're crispy, light, and delicious. This old-fashioned recipe is another adaptation from Great Grandmother Catharine's recipe that she made on the farm.", "recipe_category": ["Breakfast"], "recipe_image": ["/recipes/waffles/waffles.jpg"], "recipe_total_time": ["PT45M"], "recipe_published_time": ["Oct 21, 2011"], "image_urls": ["http://www.makebetterfood.com/recipes/waffles/waffles.jpg"], "recipe_ingredients": ["12 \u00bd ounces cake or all-purpose flour, about 2 \u00bd cups", "3 teaspoons baking powder", "\u00be teaspoon salt", "1 \u00bd tablespoons sugar", "5 eggs, separated", "6 tablespoons butter, melted", "2 \u00bc cup milk", "cooking spray", "maple syrup, honey button, or sweetened strawberries (optional)"], "recipe_prep_time": ["PT20M"], "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<title>How To Make Great Waffles - MakeBetterFood.com</title>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html;charset=utf-8\" />\n<link href=\"http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Brawler\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\n<link href=\"/css/style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\n<!--[if lte IE 7]>\n<link href=\"/css/ie7.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\"/>\n<![endif]-->\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\" />\n<link rel=\"alternate\" type=\"application/rss+xml\" title=\"MakeBetterFood.com - Recipes, Learn How to Cook Amazing Food\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/MakeBetterFood\"/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"How To Make Great Waffles\"/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"food\"/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"http://www.makebetterfood.com/recipes/waffles/\"/>\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"http://www.makebetterfood.com/recipes/waffles/waffles.jpg\"/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"MakeBetterFood.com\"/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"You'll want to let go